      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the \"it depends\" thing, but that feels like a cop out lol. like, if u look at how most of the world works today, isn't extreme nationalism basically just a precursor to war and instability? it seems like the \"unifying\" part is a bit of a stretch when you look at the actual outcomes.",
